<br>
go into the gnoll caves on the wall north of town.  Run wiith Levitation, and try to move invisible (watch for the casters) and take the right turn at every opportunity.    After the second room you should move slowly becuase when you can see the rock in the floor of the passage ahead - you're near a hidden drop off.<br>
<br>
Edge forward until you fall through the floor and float down- stay close to the wall behind you.  Ahead you'll see a gnoll.  Where he stands is where you park your pet later.<br>
<br>
Summon a pet - equip him or prepare to chain, as you prefer.  Engage the gnoll ahead, kill him and park the pet there.  At the end of the corridor is where it opens up is another - when ready pull him (with malise or annul) and kill him.  Just outside the passage to the left is another - when ready pull and kill him.<br>
<br>
the first gnoll will respawn in about 12-13 minutes... If you have time, ahead on the left wall (at the top of the hill) is another gnoll - pull and kill him.<br>
<br>
now go back to the drop off and med up.<br>
<br>
If you have KEI and a decent mana pool- you'll have time to med up before the first one pops.  This should give you a decent steady exp  flow - safe from wandering animals.<br>
